article.headline: Lopez scores 22, helps Saint Francis (PA) hold off Campbell 78-76
article.description: — Carlos Lopez Jr. had 22 points in Saint Francis (PA)'s 78-76 victory against Campbell on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Lopez scores 22, helps Saint Francis (PA) hold off Campbell 78-76
article.story: LORETTO, Pa. -- — Carlos Lopez Jr. had 22 points in Saint Francis (PA)'s 78-76 victory against Campbell on Saturday night. Lopez was 6 of 9 shooting, including 6 for 7 from 3-point range, and went 4 for 4 from the line for the Red Flash (5-8). Cam Gregory scored 18 points, going 6 of 14 from the floor, including 2 for 7 from 3-point range, and 4 for 6 from the line. Aaron Talbert was 4 of 8 shooting, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 4 from the line to finish with 12 points, while adding eight assists. Jasin Sinani led the Fighting Camels (6-7, Colonial Athletic Association) in scoring, finishing with 20 points. Anthony Dell'Orso added 12 points for Campbell. Broc Bidwell also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
